headline: GOP members to STB: Find ‘real’ benefits or reject rail merger
summary: Dozens of Senators and Representatives have urged a careful review by federal regulators of the proposed merger of Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern. The post GOP members to STB: Find ‘real’ benefits or reject rail merger appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From Norfolk Southern’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Norfolk Southern’s fourth quarter results reflected the impact of continued weakness in freight volumes and competitive pressures, with management noting that service and safety improvements were key internal achievements during a challenging period.
